# Dependencies

This program requires the following Python modules to work:
  - xmpppy: http://xmpppy.sourceforge.net/
  - bitcoin: http://gitorious.org/python-bitcoin/


# Configuration

Edit conf.py.example and rename it to conf.py.

In the 'component' section, set up the credentials that should be used
to connect as a component to the Jabber server.

The 'db' section is used to set up the file name of the SQLite
database that the program stores its persistent data in (registrations,
bitcoin addresses, users' balances, etc.).
